    "unit": "sherlock-hound-ch1",
    "level": "b2",
    "order": 2,
    "text": "I stood upon the hearth-rug and picked up the stick which our visitor had left behind him the night before.",
    "audio": "/audio/sherlock-hound-ch1/sherlock-hound-1902-c1-b2-002--n.mp3",
    "tags": ["sherlock-hound", "chapter1", "past"]
  },
  {
    "id": "sherlock-hound-1902-c1-b2-003",
    "unit": "sherlock-hound-ch1",
    "level": "b2",
    "order": 3,
    "text": "It was a fine, thick piece of wood, bulbous-headed, of the sort which is known as a Penang lawyer.",
    "audio": "/audio/sherlock-hound-ch1/sherlock-hound-1902-c1-b2-003--n.mp3",
    "tags": ["sherlock-hound", "chapter1", "description"]
